snippet.title: Lafada || लफडा ||  Episode 02 || 29 September || 2023 || Raju,Anita,Rabi,Manju || Nepali Comedy
snippet.description:
Master TV Presents:-
Lafada || लफडा ||  Episode 02 || 29 September || 2023 || Raju,Anita,Rabi,Manju || Nepali Comedy
Lafada is a fiction comedy drama. In Lafada, it is tried to present the happenings in the society in a cinematic way. Here, an attempt has been made to present the story between the ordinary people, the poor and the rulers, who are directly or indirectly affected by the politics taken as elements that disrupt the society. Lafada is written and directed by Raju Paudel.
Raju Paudel is a famous comedian of Nepal. He is currently writing and directing a teleserial called Juthe. Through Lafada, Raju will try to show the reality of the society.

snippet.title: Lafada || लफडा ||  Episode 01 || 22 September || 2023 || Raju,Anita,Rabi,Manju || Nepali Comedy
snippet.description:
Master TV Presents:-
Lafada || लफडा ||  Episode 01 || 22 September || 2023 || Raju,Anita,Rabi,Manju || Nepali Comedy
Lafada is a fiction comedy drama. In Lafada, it is tried to present the happenings in the society in a cinematic way. Here, an attempt has been made to present the story between the ordinary people, the poor and the rulers, who are directly or indirectly affected by the politics taken as elements that disrupt the society. Lafada is written and directed by Raju Paudel.
Raju Paudel is a famous comedian of Nepal. He is currently writing and directing a teleserial called Juthe. Through Lafada, Raju will try to show the reality of the society.

In this season, we bring you a fresh and dynamic mix of contestants from different walks of life, each with their own unique stories, dreams, and determination. From the auditions to the intense tasks and vote-outs, witness their journey as they push their limits, face their fears, and prove their mettle to survive the grueling Roadies journey.

Our esteemed panel of gang leaders, comprising some of the most charismatic and influential personalities, are all set to mentor and guide the contestants throughout their Roadies voyage. With their experience, knowledge, and a perfect blend of tough love and motivation, these leaders will shape the roadies into true warriors who can conquer any challenge that comes their way.

But it's not just about the tasks and the competition;  Roadies Season 19 also dives deep into the personal stories, struggles, and aspirations of the contestants. Join us as we embark on this thrilling adventure across breathtaking locations, testing the physical and mental prowess of our roadies. From nail-biting stunts to mind-boggling challenges, each episode will leave you on the edge of your seat, eagerly awaiting the next twist and turn.

snippet.title: Asian Games: Nepal's Dipendra Airee Smashes 50 Off 9 Balls, Breaks Yuvraj Singh’s Record | The Quint
snippet.description:
Dipendra Singh Airee of Nepal on Wednesday achieved the fastest fifty, taking only nine balls to break Yuvraj Singh's 16-year-old record set during the 2007 T20 World Cup match against England.

In the group match of the ongoing Asian Games, Dipendra scored an unbeaten 52 off just 10 balls against Mongolia here at the Pingfeng Cricket Field. His record knock was studded with eight sixes.

localized.title: Asian Games: Nepal's Dipendra Airee Smashes 50 Off 9 Balls, Breaks Yuvraj Singh’s Record | The Quint
localized.description:
Dipendra Singh Airee of Nepal on Wednesday achieved the fastest fifty, taking only nine balls to break Yuvraj Singh's 16-year-old record set during the 2007 T20 World Cup match against England.

In the group match of the ongoing Asian Games, Dipendra scored an unbeaten 52 off just 10 balls against Mongolia here at the Pingfeng Cricket Field. His record knock was studded with eight sixes.

In this explosive episode of Roadies Season 19, tensions reach an all-time high as Rhea takes issue with Prince's Instagram antics! 😤📱 Hashtag drama alert! 👀

😱 Rhea and Gautam find themselves in the spotlight as Prince takes to Instagram to stir the pot and sling some serious shade their way! 😡🔥

But wait, it's not all talk! When Prince starts firing back, things quickly escalate into a fiery, no-holds-barred showdown between him and Gautam! 😤🗣️

Just when it looks like an all-out brawl is about to erupt, the man of the hour, Sonu Sood, steps in to lay down the law and deliver some serious tough love to the Gang Leaders! 💪👊

The question on everyone's mind: How will this drama-packed episode affect the upcoming Vote Out? 🤔📜

Don't miss a minute of the action – tune in to this heart-pounding episode of Roadies Season 19 to find out how it all unfolds! 📺🍿

From the auditions to the intense tasks and vote-outs, witness their journey as they push their limits, face their fears, and prove their mettle to survive the grueling Roadies journey.

Join us as we embark on this thrilling adventure across breathtaking locations, testing the physical and mental prowess of our roadies. From nail-biting stunts to mind-boggling challenges, each episode will leave you on the edge of your seat, eagerly awaiting the next twist and turn.

 Roadies Season 19 is not just a reality show; it's a journey of self-discovery, resilience, and triumph. It's a celebration of the human spirit and the unwavering belief that with determination and perseverance, anything is possible.

snippet.description:
𝙋𝘼𝙍𝙄𝙒𝘼𝙍 is a Nepali Family Drama TV serial broadcasting every Wednesday on Galaxy 4K TV at 7:00 PM & YouTube at 7:30 PM. The show (𝙋𝘼𝙍𝙄𝙒𝘼𝙍) is Writers, Director & Produced by Saroj Ghimire. The story is based on a rural lifestyle and lower middle-class people. The show stars Deshbhakta Khanal, Hiuwala Gautam, Sushil Pokharel, Ghanshyam Joshi, Sujit Thapa, Asmita Basnet, Saroj Ghimire, Radha Shrestha, Diya GC, Aarati Lama as the main character.
